We're thrilled to have **124 registrations** so far from passionate learners worldwide who are ready to transform water, sanitation, and hygiene data into actionable insights! üìä


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}
![](index_files/figure-html/plot-country-1.png){width=672}
