**üó∫ Global reach, diverse perspectives:** Our participants span continents, with African countries leading the way. We have 15 registrations from Ghana, followed by strong representation from Uganda (13 registrations), Switzerland (10 registrations) and Ethiopia (10 registrations). Also very exciting to see a strong female participation with 36% of the registrations. You're creating an inclusive learning environment where diverse voices will enrich our experience. ü§ù


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}
![](index_files/figure-html/plot-population-pyramid-1.png){width=768}
:::
:::


**üìö Meeting learners at every level:** While 70% of participants hold advanced degrees and 48% are employed full-time, 86% are beginners in R programming. This mix creates a unique learning environment where everyone brings valuable perspectives. Whether you're taking your first steps in coding or bringing years of WASH expertise we're ready to support you in this path of adding data science to your toolkit. üíª‚ú®





