**ü§ñ AI-powered learning:** With 100% of participants already using AI tools (most popular: ChatGPT, Gemini, Copilot for Microsoft 365), we're excited to include our bonus module: **"Use of AI for coding support"**. This module will help all participants - from beginners to experienced coders - leverage AI tools effectively and responsibly in their data science journey.


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}
